synopsis: Warn if expected files are omitted from extra-doc-files
packages: Cabal
prs: #8657
issues: #3964

description: {

- Emit a warning if there is no “changelog” file at the root of the package or
  it is not included in the field “extra-doc-files”. 
- Emit a warning if a “changelog” file at the root of the package is included 
  in a field different from “extra-doc-files”.
}